    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. when you say there is a \"growing recognition\" and a \"consensus,\" does that mean the debates around things like gender-affirming care for minors or certain sports policies are basically settled from a scientific standpoint, or is there still real disagreement about how this should be applied in the real world?",
